            "title": "即月期指開報26420點 低水99點",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">即月期指開報26420點，跌64點，較上日現貨收市價26518點低水99點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">即月科指期貨開報9307點，跌4點，低水16點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">即月國指期貨開報9400點，跌27點，低水43點。</p>\n</div>",
